edu.cmu.ri.rcommerce.sensor
Class MapConstrainMeasurer<P extends Particle2D>

java.lang.Object
  edu.cmu.ri.rcommerce.sensor.MapConstrainMeasurer<P>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Measurer<P>
public class MapConstrainMeasurer<P extends Particle2D>
extends Object
implements Measurer<P>

Extension of RSSIMeasurer which kills particles that are out of bounds on the map by setting their weights to 0. This should improve convergence by eliminating impossible states.

Author:
Nisarg
